## v1 â†’ v2 Changes

| Feature | v1 | v2 |
|---------|----|----|
| Self-correction | Documentation only | Executable CorrectionLoop |
| Context tracking | None | Full state history + drift detection |
| Validation | None | Configurable rule engine |
| Metrics | None | Iteration-level tracking + JSON export |
| CLI | Setup scripts only | init / status / report |
| Tests | None | Full pytest suite |
| Install | Not a package | pip installable |

